                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-script">
                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/symfony/edit/master/knpu/extra-doctrine-collections/removing-items.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>Back on the Genus page, I want to add a little "X" icon next to each user. When
we click that, it will make an AJAX call that will remove the scientist from
this <code>Genus</code>.</p>
<h2 id="how-a-manytomany-link-is-removed">How a ManyToMany Link is Removed <a class="headerlink" href="removing-items#how-a-manytomany-link-is-removed" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
