<h2 id="the-remove-endpoint-setup">The Remove Endpoint Setup <a class="headerlink" href="removing-items#the-remove-endpoint-setup" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Inside, we need to make an AJAX call back to our app. Let's go set that up.
Open <code>GenusController</code> and find some space for a new method:
<code>public function removeGenusScientistAction()</code>. Give it an <code>@Route()</code> set to
<code>/genus/{genusId}/scientist/{userId}</code>:</p>
