<h2 id="deleting-the-link">Deleting the Link <a class="headerlink" href="removing-items#deleting-the-link" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Now <em>all</em> we need to do is remove the <code>User</code> from the <code>Genus</code>. We don't have a method
to do that yet, so right below <code>addGenusScientist()</code>, make a new public function
called <code>removeGenusScientist()</code> with a <code>User</code> argument:</p>
