<h2 id="returning-from-the-endpoint">Returning from the Endpoint <a class="headerlink" href="removing-items#returning-from-the-endpoint" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>At the bottom, we still need to return a Response. But, there's not really any information
we need to send back to our JavaScript... so I'm going to return a <code>new Response</code>
with <code>null</code> as the content and a 204 status code:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="92f883ef4e">
